# Prints the given text inside a red box to STDERR. Text must be passed in
# either as an argument or via STDIN.
#
#     box-err error message through arguments
#     box-err 'error message through quoted argument'
#     box-err <<EOT
#     error message through STDIN and a HEREDOC
#     EOT
box "${BOX_RED}" "$@" >&2
